    hardscapeStylePara: "NYC hardscape style runs to bluestone patios with Belgian-block edging in brownstone yards, precast unit pavers in Queens and Staten Island single-family, and boardwalk-style pressure-treated decks in Brooklyn rowhome gardens. Cast-iron garden furniture is period-correct for Park Slope and Brooklyn Heights Victorian-era lots. Permeable-paver driveways are encouraged under NYC DEP stormwater rules and qualify for the Green Infrastructure Grant Program up to $25,000.",
